      "id": "5a93c517_8e891e77",
      "file_path": "INFO.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 30,
      "message": "Just curious about the timezone \"America/Michigan\"?  Most of MIchigan is in the Eastern timezone, but there are parts of the Upper Peninsula that are in Central.  This doesn't seem specific enough.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 33,
        "name": "James Forsyth",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jf2512@att.com",
        "username": "jimmydot"
      },
      "updated": "2018-02-23 20:05:31.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "5a93c517_ee73027e",
      "file_path": "INFO.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 41,
      "message": "Steve Smokowski worked on the OpenECOMP version of AAI but moved on before the ONAP project committer list was defined; he is not listed as a committer on the Resources and Repositories wiki page.  @Gildas, do I need to make a formal request of the TSC for this, or can this committer just be removed?  I have confirmation from Steve that is OK being removed.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 33,
        "name": "James Forsyth",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jf2512@att.com",
        "username": "jimmydot"
